Package: statxplorerplus
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Stat-Xplore Style Specs, Labels, and JSON Conversion
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Your", family = "Name", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "you@example.com"))
Description: Helper utilities to transform Stat-Xplore-style JSON specs to/from tables,
    resolve labels to IDs via API schema traversal, update spec tables to latest available
    dates, and export corrected JSON for downstream use.
